modShortDescription: Just a small mod that increases the number of skill points you get per level. Customizable by changing the XML file.
modDescription:
Just a small mod that increases the number of [skill points](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-skill-points/) you get per level. Customizable by changing the XML file.

**[Download](https://docs.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1t4M3dnJStzzAyPzKoq76rCjp3lM-ETX1)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/19748-aarong85s-a19-modlets/).
